OL,3,CMother and brother deny killing
OL,4,Cteenager in house fire
OL,6,FThe mother and brother of a teenager
OL,7,Fwho died in a house fire have denied
OL,8,Fkilling her and abstracting
OL,9,Felectricity in the run-up to the blaze.
OL,11,FLeah Casson, 18, died following the
OL,12,Ffire at her home in Vicarage Street in
OL,13,FNorth Shields on January 16 2023.
OL,15,FHer mother Danielle Johnson, 43, and
OL,16,Fbrother Louis Casson, 19, of Whitley
OL,17,FRoad, Holystone, North Tyneside,
OL,18,Fappeared at Newcastle Crown Court to
OL,19,Fdeny manslaughter.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
