OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1779700300
OL,3,CMother and brother deny killing
OL,4,Cteenager in house fire
OL,6,FThey appeared alongside Calvin Smith,
OL,7,F37, of Peregrine Court, North Shields,
OL,8,Fwho also denied manslaughter.
OL,10,FJohnson and Smith also denied
OL,11,Fabstracting electricity from August
OL,12,Fand November 2022.
OL,14,FAll three defendants pleaded not
OL,15,Fguilty to abstracting electricity from
OL,16,FNovember 2022 to January 2023, when
OL,17,Fthe fatal fire happened.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
